  "remarks": "CFi.004 Designation: Chief Corporal of the Forces Armées Centrafricaines (FACA). Has controlled and commanded a large group of armed militia men. Father’s name (adoptive father) is Ekatom Saragba (also spelled Yekatom Saragba). Brother of Yves Saragba, an anti-Balaka commander in Batalimo, Lobaye province, and a former FACA soldier. Physical description: eye colour: black; hair colour: bold; complexion: black; height: 170cm; weight: 100kg.; Listing: Listed on 20 Aug. 2015 (amended on 28 Jul. 2020)",
